headline: Upbeat April Jobs Data Put Focus on 3 Sector ETFs & Stocks
summary: The U.S. economy added 177,000 jobs in April 2025, a slowdown from the downwardly revised 185,000 in March, but significantly surpassing market expectations of 130,000.
